106
00:07:39,826 --> 00:07:43,663
So I had served on a
couple of the boards,

107
00:07:43,696 --> 00:07:45,665
I was active in the youth group.

108
00:07:45,698 --> 00:07:47,233
I played the drums
in the worship team,

109
00:07:47,266 --> 00:07:50,236
I sang in the choir.

110
00:07:50,269 --> 00:07:53,105
