Sundays and things like that.

111
00:07:53,139 --> 00:07:57,543
So not just church, but my
faith was really important.

112
00:07:57,577 --> 00:08:02,582
And I had gone one year with
my dad to an annual conference.

113
00:08:07,653 --> 00:08:10,790
I was always interested
in law and in politics.

114
00:08:10,823 --> 00:08:12,925
And he thought this
is, essentially,

115
00:08:12,959 --> 00:08:15,561
a legislative body, so you'll
find it really fascinating

116
00:08:15,595 --> 00:08:17,763
how they vote on legislation.

117
00:08:17,797 --> 00:08:19,999
It just so happened,
in that year,

118
00:08:20,032 --> 00:08:22,902
