floor about homosexuality.

119
00:08:22,935 --> 00:08:26,239
An LGBT related piece
of legislation came up

120
00:08:26,272 --> 00:08:30,343
and there was really some
tough debate around that.

121
00:08:30,376 --> 00:08:32,912
I'd say 80% of those
