140
00:09:25,898 --> 00:09:28,768
And I had never
thought about it.

141
00:09:28,801 --> 00:09:30,970
And I just said
I don't think so.

142
00:09:31,003 --> 00:09:33,839
I mean, I guess he could
be, but I don't know.

143
00:09:33,873 --> 00:09:36,208
He was withdrawn, at that time.

144
00:09:36,242 --> 00:09:39,245
He kind of went from school,
straight up to his room

145
00:09:39,278 --> 00:09:41,147
and he didn't really talk.

146
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:42,949
And before, we always hung out.

147
00:09:42,982 --> 00:09:44,750
And I thought, well, it's
just being a teenager.

148
00:09:44,784 --> 00:09:47,386
He just needs this
time by himself.

149
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:49,689
I had seen a friend of
mine come out to his family

150
00:09:49,722 --> 00:09:51,390
and his family kicked
him out of the house.

151
00:09:51,424 --> 00:09:54,427
His mother even said to him,
