break my neck and die.

166
00:10:40,806 --> 00:10:43,376
My daughter came home
from school one day,

167
00:10:43,409 --> 00:10:47,013
and she was very
upset and crying.

168
00:10:47,046 --> 00:10:51,250
Tim was telling her that
he thought he was gay

169
00:10:51,283 --> 00:10:54,487
and he was considering suicide.

170
00:10:54,520 --> 00:10:58,891
I felt strongly that the
parents should be notified,

171
00:10:58,924 --> 00:11:02,395
