175
00:11:11,370 --> 00:11:13,139
I received this phone call.

176
00:11:13,172 --> 00:11:17,276
I said my daughter was
friends with his son.

177
00:11:17,309 --> 00:11:22,248
He was gay and that he believed
that being gay was wrong

178
00:11:22,281 --> 00:11:25,751
