195
00:12:11,297 --> 00:12:12,231
Is it true?

196
00:12:12,264 --> 00:12:13,199
Are you gay?

197
00:12:13,232 --> 00:12:16,902
I had this phone
conversation with this lady.

198
00:12:16,936 --> 00:12:18,904
I must have hesitated
for quite a while,

199
00:12:18,938 --> 00:12:21,407
and I was going over
my options in my head.

200
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:25,277
I can tell them the truth or
I can laugh it off and lie.

201
00:12:25,311 --> 00:12:26,912
And I had thought,
you know what?

202
00:12:26,946 --> 00:12:27,880
I'm just going to tell them.

203
00:12:27,913 --> 00:12:29,515
We embraced him that night.

204
00:12:29,548 --> 00:12:32,184
And we just, and I remember
there were a lot of tears.

205
00:12:32,218 --> 00:12:33,986
We were all in tears,
all three of us.

206
00:12:34,019 --> 00:12:37,556
And then we said,
