love you, no matter what.

208
00:12:40,459 --> 00:12:44,864
He had struggled all this time
and I never knew about it.

209
00:12:44,897 --> 00:12:47,299
And he was all alone in this.

210
00:12:47,333 --> 00:12:49,969
It wasn't that I was
gay that had upset him.

211
00:12:50,002 --> 00:12:51,904
It was that I felt
I couldn't share

212
00:12:51,937 --> 00:12:53,072
with them a part of who I was.

213
00:12:56,442 --> 00:12:59,578
I do remember asking him why
he didn't feel comfortable

214
00:12:59,612 --> 00:13:01,947
