235
00:14:22,661 --> 00:14:25,097
I was extremely excited.

236
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:28,534
I thought this was going
to be a significant victory

237
00:14:28,567 --> 00:14:31,003
for the whole church.

238
00:14:31,036 --> 00:14:32,538
